{"tid":1446033,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"810咪玩得幾好囉 811又番返轉頭","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T23:52:02.000Z","uid":282782,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab5245ecdb4c24a3f73994d0eb0da6b61f90f19","tid":1446033,"uid":282782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:41:09.000Z","msg":"其實我真係唔係好明 <br />\n昨日大埔 一齊走咗幾轉場<br />\n雖然途中有幾次<br />\n因為目的地有啲信息上嘅混亂<br />\n但全程又能到狗 又封到路<br />\n新手又玩到 和理非都可參與<br />\n去到某啲位勇武又可以𨶙陣狗<br />\n啲狗又唔點捉到人<br />\n今日好似返番晒轉頭<br />\n係荔枝角為咩而守<br />\n守唔係認真守 一嘢就又走晒<br />\n上到車又無討論目的地<br />\n到咗tst又突去狗屋唔知守咩<br />\n今日仲要面對狗仔嘅各種新招捉人<br />\n點解會突又玩𨶙番轉頭！！！！<br />\n<br />\n仲有出面吹勇武可抖下可唔可以收收皮！<br />\n如果統和理非攪得掂今時今日<br />\n就唔駛攪成咁<br />\n今日個爆咗眼嘅女仔<br />\n每個有去發夢嘅人都有責任！！"},{"pid":"3da5651f602144bf50e3d832943c4ae3c51b709e","tid":1446033,"uid":282782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:45:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3485a559425a97d5a1b759d651b203a9e85d73e2","tid":1446033,"uid":282782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:46:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e23fed6a71c9384f420517fa673bab366ee6f6b","tid":1446033,"uid":28960,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"今日好撚多鬼&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;唔係次次防到"},{"pid":"8edb8a056694b2fd168477c78b711c36ab33a7b2","tid":1446033,"uid":282782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e23fed6a71c9384f420517fa673bab366ee6f6b","tid":1446033,"uid":28960,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"今日好撚多鬼&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;唔係次次防到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"所以昨日嗰個模式咁咪幾好"},{"pid":"be64afdcf191974f5b421b6bcf489bf22c188494","tid":1446033,"uid":282782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:49:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"527daa4458f4fa84223b0e4fdea13776872ac38b","tid":1446033,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi